  {}
}

body:multipart-form {
  message: Comment with attached photos
  type: user
  files: @file(/Users/samutpra/Pictures/logo.png)
  files: @file(/Users/samutpra/Pictures/logo_CARMEN_Classic-Blue_low-res.png)
}

vars:pre-request {
  purchase_request_template_id: 5d5fa453-f687-4fcd-bbdb-5956f7e810b3
}

docs {
  ## Create Purchase Request Template Comment (with file uploads)
  สร้างความคิดเห็นใหม่สำหรับ purchase-request-template พร้อมแนบไฟล์ใน request เดียว
  ไม่ต้อง upload file แยกก่อน

  Creates a new comment for a purchase-request-template with optional file attachments in a single multipart request. `purchase_request_template_id` is specified via URL path parameter, not in the body.

  ### Path Parameters
  | Name | Type | Description |
  |------|------|-------------|
  | `bu_code` | string | Business unit code |
  | `purchase_request_template_id` | string (UUID) | Purchase Request Template ID |

  ### Headers
  | Name | Required | Description |
  |------|----------|-------------|
  | `Authorization` | Yes | `Bearer {{access_token}}` |
  | `x-app-id` | Yes | `{{x_app_id}}` |

  ### Permissions
  > Permission key not found in seed; review needed.

  ### Sample Body (multipart/form-data)
  | Field | Type | Required | Description |
  |-------|------|----------|-------------|
  | `message` | text | Conditional | Comment text (≤ 4000 chars). Required if no files. |
  | `type` | text | No | `user` (default) or `system` |
  | `files` | binary (repeatable) | Conditional | Attachments. Required if no message. |

  Constraints: max 10 files, max 10 MB per file, allowed: image/jpeg, image/png, image/webp, image/gif, application/pdf.

  ### Sample Response
  ```json
  {
    "data": {
      "id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4d",
      "purchase_request_template_id": "019638a6-2a00-7c4f-8e46-9b7a52c80c4e",
      "message": "Template updated for Q2 season.",
      "type": "user",
      "attachments": [
        {
          "fileName": "photo.jpg",
          "fileToken": "tok-abc-123",
          "fileUrl": "",
          "contentType": "image/jpeg",
          "size": 204800
        }
      ]
    },
    "paginate": null,
    "status": 201,
    "success": true,
    "message": "Success",
    "timestamp": "2026-04-29T08:30:00.000Z"
  }
  ```

  > Note: `fileUrl` ใน response จะว่าง — frontend ต้องเรียก
  > `GET /api/{bu_code}/documents/presigned-url/{fileToken}` เพื่อแสดงไฟล์

  ### Error Responses
  | Status | When |
  |--------|------|
  | 400 | Neither `message` nor `files` provided; file count/size/mime exceeds limit |
  | 401 | Missing or invalid Bearer token |
  | 502 | File service (S3 upload) upstream failure |

  > Service-layer errors propagate via TCP; see micro-business for full list.
}
